WEBVTT

00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:08.066
Why cover your face?

00:00:08.066 --> 00:00:09.166
I owe you money.

00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:12.233
You don't owe me money, but you owe me something else.

00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:14.933
Tell me less.

00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:16.600
How can you refund my gas card?

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.033
So what are you in the hurry for?

00:00:18.466 --> 00:00:19.666
Go take a bath.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.233
Take a shower and talk later.

00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:22.900
Why take a bath?

00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.400
Look at her.

00:00:24.966 --> 00:00:25.833
Sincerely

00:00:47.566 --> 00:00:49.000
Why are you wearing my wife's clothes?

00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:50.466
This is my house.

00:00:50.466 --> 00:00:52.066
No my bachelorette clothes.

00:00:52.166 --> 00:00:53.066
Good.

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:54.633
This is more interesting.

00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:57.033
I don't want to talk to you about this right now.

00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.166
I took a shower as you requested.

00:00:59.166 --> 00:01:01.300
Now we can get to work.

00:01:03.066 --> 00:01:04.866
This is not the place for formal discussion.

00:01:06.866 --> 00:01:08.166
Go to bedroom.